spanGrp.span: There are Churches of St. George, Saint Maria’s, of St. Haralambos and of St. Paul in our village.

When there were the holy days everyone were coming to celebrate.
The priest was giving a sacrament.
We would light candles in churches and we were having a good time.
There were nice trees and fruits such as apple trees and plum trees in our village.
